{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/harry-potter-hogwarts-mystery-game-rpg-harry-potter-untuk-smartphone/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Harry Potter Hogwarts Mystery: Game RPG Harry Potter untuk Smartphone","content":"<p><strong>Oleh: @HarryRezqiano</strong></p>\n<p><em>Franchise</em> Harry Potter sudah beredar lama di dunia. IP yang bercerita soal dunia penyihir seru ini diciptakan oleh pengarang novel J.K Rowling yang berkebangsaan Inggris sejak tahun 1997.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44733\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44733\" data-attachment-id=\"44733\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemula-di-tekken-gunakan-saja-karakter-petarung-ini-di-debut-tinju-besi-kalian/attachment/har5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Novelis sukses dari Inggris, J.K Rowling (Sumber gambar: thisisinsider.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Novelis sukses dari Inggris, J.K Rowling (Sumber gambar: thisisinsider.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44733\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har5.jpg\" alt=\"Novelis sukses dari Inggris, J.K Rowling (Sumber gambar: thisisinsider.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44733\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Novelis sukses dari Inggris, J.K Rowling (Sumber gambar: thisisinsider.com)</p></div>\n<p>Harry Potter merupakan serial novel super sukses di dunia yang sudah terjual lebih dari 400 juta buku dan terus bertambah. Sejak seri pertama novel Harry Potter yang berjudul “Harry Potter and the Philosopher’s Stone” diterbitkan di Inggris 26 Juni 1997, rangkaian kepopuleran dari IP ini menggurita hingga ke berbagai lini seperti film, <em>merchandise, theme park</em>, dan banyak lagi produk lainnya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44737\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44737\" data-attachment-id=\"44737\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemula-di-tekken-gunakan-saja-karakter-petarung-ini-di-debut-tinju-besi-kalian/attachment/har9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Wahana taman bermain Harry Potter / Hogwarts (Sumber gambar: telegraph.co.uk)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Wahana taman bermain Harry Potter / Hogwarts (Sumber gambar: telegraph.co.uk)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har9-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har9.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44737\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har9.jpg\" alt=\"Wahana taman bermain Harry Potter / Hogwarts (Sumber gambar: telegraph.co.uk)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har9.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har9-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44737\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Wahana taman bermain Harry Potter / Hogwarts (Sumber gambar: telegraph.co.uk)</p></div>\n<p>Dan, tentu saja, termasuk <em>video games</em> bertema Harry Potter. Ada banyak <em>video games</em> bertema dunia Harry Potter diciptakan. Sebenarnya tidak hanya <em>video game; game</em> jenis <em>‘board game’</em> dengan tema Harry Potter pun ada dibuat dan sama larisnya dengan <em>video game</em>, yang merupakan mainan elektronik. Tercatat ada 13 jenis <em>video game</em> yang diciptakan dan bertema dunia Harry Potter beredar sejak 2001.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44729\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44729\" data-attachment-id=\"44729\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemula-di-tekken-gunakan-saja-karakter-petarung-ini-di-debut-tinju-besi-kalian/attachment/har1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Board Game Harry Potter (Sumber gambar: geekandsundry.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Board Game Harry Potter (Sumber gambar: geekandsundry.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44729\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har1.jpg\" alt=\"Board Game Harry Potter (Sumber gambar: geekandsundry.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44729\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Board Game Harry Potter (Sumber gambar: geekandsundry.com)</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_44738\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44738\" data-attachment-id=\"44738\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemula-di-tekken-gunakan-saja-karakter-petarung-ini-di-debut-tinju-besi-kalian/attachment/har10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har10.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Harry Potter dalam format video game (Sumber gambar: kotaku.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Harry Potter dalam format video game (Sumber gambar: kotaku.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har10-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har10.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44738\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har10.jpg\" alt=\"Harry Potter dalam format video game (Sumber gambar: kotaku.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har10.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har10-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44738\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Harry Potter dalam format video game (Sumber gambar: kotaku.com)</p></div>\n<p>Dimulai dari <em>game</em> “Harry Potter and the Philosopher’s Stone” yang muncul secara <em>multiplatform</em> alias ada di semua <em>console</em> tahun 2001 (PS1, PS2, Xbox, GameCube, Game Boy Color, Game Boy Advance hingga ke Windows PC dan Apple Mac) sampai yang sebentar lagi akan muncul di tahun 2018 ini. Game untuk platform smartphone iOS dan Android berjudul “Harry Potter: Hogwarts Mystery”.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44731\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44731\" data-attachment-id=\"44731\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemula-di-tekken-gunakan-saja-karakter-petarung-ini-di-debut-tinju-besi-kalian/attachment/har3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Game Official (Sumber gambar: pickedbox.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Game Official (Sumber gambar: pickedbox.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44731\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har3.jpg\" alt=\"Game Official (Sumber gambar: pickedbox.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44731\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Game Official (Sumber gambar: pickedbox.com)</p></div>\n<p>Pertama kali diumumkan pada 18 January 2018, Hogwarts Mystery merupakan <em>game</em> Harry Potter yang akan mengambil tema<em> role-playing game</em> alias RPG. Tapi karena akan muncul di smartphone, <em>game</em> ini mungkin akan menggunakan ‘rute sederhana’ untuk <em>gameplay</em> serta kualitas grafis. <em>Game</em> RPG smartphone sebenarnya nggak jelek-jelek amat jika <em>developer game</em>-nya tahu apa yang mereka kerjakan.</p>\n<p>Final Fantasy XV Pocket Edition contohnya. Game Final Fantasy XV versi console dan PC memang terlihat ‘wah!’ dan cakep banget. Mustahil mencapai level grafis seperti itu di smartphone yang jelas-jelas tidak sekuat PC ataupun console.</p>\n<p>Jadi saat Square Enix mem-port Final Fantasy XV ke platform <em>smartphone</em>, mereka melakukan <em>overhaul</em> dan modifikasi <em>engine</em> agar <em>game</em> Final Fantasy XV di <em>smartphone</em> tetap dapat menarik dan memukau walau grafisnyaa jelas akan lebih lemah dibandingkan versi <em>console</em> maupun PC. Dan mereka berhasil. Final Fantasy XV <em>Pocket Edition</em> terlihat keren banget; tentunya untuk ukuran<em> game</em> RPG di <em>smartphone</em> masa kini.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44730\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44730\" data-attachment-id=\"44730\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemula-di-tekken-gunakan-saja-karakter-petarung-ini-di-debut-tinju-besi-kalian/attachment/har2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Final Fantasy XV. Versi console di kiri, versi smartphone di kanan (Sumber gambar: gametransfers.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Final Fantasy XV. Versi console di kiri, versi smartphone di kanan (Sumber gambar: gametransfers.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44730\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har2.jpg\" alt=\"Final Fantasy XV. Versi console di kiri, versi smartphone di kanan (Sumber gambar: gametransfers.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44730\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Final Fantasy XV. Versi console di kiri, versi smartphone di kanan (Sumber gambar: gametransfers.com)</p></div>\n<p>Harry Potter: Hogwarts Mystery memiliki plot cerita yang dimulai dari lahirnya Harry Potter. Yang berarti saat sebelum dia dijemput oleh Hagrid dari rumah Keluarga Dursley dan menjalani masa sekolahnya di Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry. Tentu saja belum ada detail lebih lengkap dan jelas selain informasi tadi karena <em>game</em>-nya juga masih dalam proses penyelesaian.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44732\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44732\" data-attachment-id=\"44732\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemula-di-tekken-gunakan-saja-karakter-petarung-ini-di-debut-tinju-besi-kalian/attachment/har4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot beta version Hogwarts Mystery (Sumber gambar: androidpolice.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Screenshot beta version Hogwarts Mystery (Sumber gambar: androidpolice.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44732\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har4.jpg\" alt=\"Screenshot beta version Hogwarts Mystery (Sumber gambar: androidpolice.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44732\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Screenshot beta version Hogwarts Mystery (Sumber gambar: androidpolice.com)</p></div>\n<p><em>Game</em> ini di-<em>develop</em> oleh <em>developer</em> bernama Jam City. Mereka adalah <em>developer game</em> untuk <em>mobile/smartphone</em> yang berbasis di Los Angeles, Amerika Serikat. Jam City terlibat di pembuatan <em>game mobile/smartphone</em> seperti Marvel Avengers Academy, Cookie Jam ataupun Panda Pop.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44735\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44735\" data-attachment-id=\"44735\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemula-di-tekken-gunakan-saja-karakter-petarung-ini-di-debut-tinju-besi-kalian/attachment/har7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber gambar: marvel.wikia.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: marvel.wikia.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44735\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har7.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber gambar: marvel.wikia.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44735\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: marvel.wikia.com</p></div>\n<p>Seperti kebanyakan <em>developer game smartphone</em> lainnya, Jam City menawarkan <em>game</em> mereka dengan konsep ‘Freemium’ alias ‘gratisan yang berbayar’. Ini merupakan mekanisme pemasaran game mobile/smartphone yang sudah normal dilakukan. <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/saat-nintendo-menyerah-pada-popularitas-smartphone/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bahkan oleh Nintendo sekalipun</a>. Sementara mereka pada dasarnya bahkan bukan<em> developer</em> atau <em>publisher game smartphone</em>!</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44734\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44734\" data-attachment-id=\"44734\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemula-di-tekken-gunakan-saja-karakter-petarung-ini-di-debut-tinju-besi-kalian/attachment/har6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Gratis. Tapi bayar (Sumber gambar: chipchick.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Gratis. Tapi bayar (Sumber gambar: chipchick.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44734\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har6.jpg\" alt=\"Gratis. Tapi bayar (Sumber gambar: chipchick.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44734\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gratis. Tapi bayar (Sumber gambar: chipchick.com)</p></div>\n<p>Info lainnya dari<em> game</em> Hogwarts Mystery ini adalah, karakter dalam <em>game</em> akan kita ciptakan sendiri dengan sistem <em>Create-A-Player</em>. Ini bisa jadi merupakan hal pertama kalinya terjadi di <em>game-game</em> Harry Potter, di mana karakter utama dalam<em> game</em> bukanlah karakter utama dari buku/novel. Di trailer singkat yang beredar untuk Hogwarts Mystery ini juga terlihat hal-hal yang menjadi khas dari dunia Harry Potter seperti pemilihan asrama oleh <em>Sorting Hat</em> hingga mempelajari penggunaan tongkat sihir serta belajar soal ramuan.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xAulFHyjFAI\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Hal lain yang menarik dari Hogwarts Mystery adalah publisher <em>game</em> ini: Portkey Games. Portkey Games adalah divisi<em> game</em> bentukan Warner Bros. <em>Interactive Entertainment</em>. Portkey Games diciptakan khusus untuk menangani <em>game-game</em> bertema dunia Harry Potter. Jadi boleh dibilang kalau Warner Bros. cukup serius menangani <em>franchise</em> Harry Potter dalam format <em>video game</em> dengan langkah tersebut.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44736\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44736\" data-attachment-id=\"44736\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pemula-di-tekken-gunakan-saja-karakter-petarung-ini-di-debut-tinju-besi-kalian/attachment/har8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Akhirnya… Kesempatan menjadi murid Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry (Sumber gambar: wix.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Akhirnya… Kesempatan menjadi murid Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry (Sumber gambar: wix.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44736\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har8.jpg\" alt=\"Akhirnya… Kesempatan menjadi murid Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry (Sumber gambar: wix.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/har8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44736\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Akhirnya… Kesempatan menjad